<div style="position:absolute;left:157.30px;top:50.94px" class="cls_009"><span class="cls_009">angels, but if I have no love, my speech is no more</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:198.64px;top:67.01px" class="cls_009"><span class="cls_009">than a noisy gong or a clanging bell.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:245.69px;top:99.24px" class="cls_009"><span class="cls_009">(1 Corinthians 13:1)</span></div>
