<div style="position:absolute;left:36.72px;top:513.72px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">1.  </span><span class="cls_011">NEGATIVE SENTENCE</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:210.39px;top:513.72px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">The shorter form is used the most.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:66.72px;top:527.52px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">(present)</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:133.43px;top:527.52px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">I do not</span></div>
