<div style="position:absolute;left:206.75px;top:568.92px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">The short form is used the most in the future.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:144.72px;top:582.72px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">I will</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:216.80px;top:582.72px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">=</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:252.81px;top:582.72px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">I'll</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:360.78px;top:582.72px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">We will</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:447.18px;top:582.72px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">=</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:495.99px;top:582.72px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">We'll</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:144.72px;top:596.52px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">You will</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:216.76px;top:596.52px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">=</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:252.76px;top:596.52px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">You'll</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:360.72px;top:596.52px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">You will</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:445.13px;top:596.52px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">=</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:493.90px;top:596.52px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">You'll</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:144.72px;top:610.32px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">He will</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:216.81px;top:610.32px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">=</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:252.80px;top:610.32px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">He'll</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:360.82px;top:610.32px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">They will</span></div>
