<div style="position:absolute;left:340.91px;top:58.76px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">Can you work there?</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:183.42px;top:70.27px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">He can't remember.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:340.91px;top:70.28px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">Can't he remember?</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:183.42px;top:102.06px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">They could drink.</span></div>
