<div style="position:absolute;left:361.47px;top:726.90px" class="cls_014"><span class="cls_014">We were poor.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:469.48px;top:726.90px" class="cls_014"><span class="cls_014">I wasn't poor.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:59.52px;top:739.56px" class="cls_014"><span class="cls_014">(future)</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:109.44px;top:739.56px" class="cls_014"><span class="cls_014">Will you be angry?   Won't he be angry?</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:364.04px;top:739.56px" class="cls_014"><span class="cls_014">She'll be angry.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:469.49px;top:739.56px" class="cls_014"><span class="cls_014">They won't be angry.</span></div>
