<div style="position:absolute;left:36.72px;top:517.27px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">a.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:58.65px;top:517.27px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">You can use WOULD or COULD instead of CAN.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:108.72px;top:528.79px" class="cls_005"><span class="cls_005">Would</span><span class="cls_012"> you please tell me how to contact her?</span></div>
