<div style="position:absolute;left:288.73px;top:712.75px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">I'm calling to check how much it costs to fly to New York..</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:108.71px;top:724.27px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">I'm calling to order a pizza.</span></div>
