<div style="position:absolute;left:321.08px;top:588.54px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">We can't </span><span class="cls_053">v</span><span class="cls_011">.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:82.62px;top:602.22px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">Can they open it?</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:321.14px;top:602.22px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">Yes, they can open it.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:321.12px;top:616.02px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">No, they can't open it.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:82.62px;top:629.82px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">Can't she wait?</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:321.13px;top:629.82px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">No, she can't wait.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:321.12px;top:643.62px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">Yes, she can wait.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:82.62px;top:657.42px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">What can you play?</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:321.10px;top:657.42px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">I can play baseball.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:82.62px;top:671.22px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">When can he come back?</span></div>
