<div style="position:absolute;left:324.73px;top:409.20px" class="cls_014"><span class="cls_014">I was going to bring him.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:86.22px;top:421.79px" class="cls_014"><span class="cls_014">When was he going to go back?</span></div>
