<div style="position:absolute;left:113.19px;top:459.84px" class="cls_015"><span class="cls_015">+ Is he going to </span><span class="cls_051">v</span><span class="cls_015">?</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:352.32px;top:459.84px" class="cls_015"><span class="cls_015">He's going to </span><span class="cls_051">v</span><span class="cls_015">.</span></div>
