<div style="position:absolute;left:324.73px;top:662.15px" class="cls_014"><span class="cls_014">I'm going to be staying at the hotel.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:86.22px;top:674.81px" class="cls_014"><span class="cls_014">When is she going to be calling?</span></div>
