<div style="position:absolute;left:324.78px;top:330.84px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">No, there wasn't any need to study it.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:36.72px;top:358.56px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">PAST</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:113.23px;top:358.56px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">+ Did they need to </span><span class="cls_053">v</span><span class="cls_011">?</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:348.72px;top:358.56px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">She needed to </span><span class="cls_053">v</span><span class="cls_011">.</span></div>
