<div style="position:absolute;left:86.23px;top:652.98px" class="cls_014"><span class="cls_014">When do they come over to help?</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:324.75px;top:652.98px" class="cls_014"><span class="cls_014">They come over to help on Monday.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:86.23px;top:665.57px" class="cls_014"><span class="cls_014">Where does he go to smoke?</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:324.73px;top:664.56px" class="cls_014"><span class="cls_014">He goes to smoke outside.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:36.72px;top:678.24px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">FUTURE</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:110.26px;top:678.24px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">+ Will you go to </span><span class="cls_053">v</span><span class="cls_011">?</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:324.72px;top:678.24px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">He'll go to </span><span class="cls_053">v</span><span class="cls_011">.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:113.22px;top:692.04px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">- Won't they come to </span><span class="cls_053">v</span><span class="cls_011">?</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:324.72px;top:692.04px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">You won't come to </span><span class="cls_053">v</span><span class="cls_011">.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:86.22px;top:705.84px" class="cls_014"><span class="cls_014">Will she come out to practice?</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:324.73px;top:705.84px" class="cls_014"><span class="cls_014">No, she won't come out to practice.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:86.22px;top:718.50px" class="cls_014"><span class="cls_014">Where will he go to study?</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:324.72px;top:718.50px" class="cls_014"><span class="cls_014">He'll go to study in the library.</span></div>
