<div style="position:absolute;left:324.72px;top:535.74px" class="cls_015"><span class="cls_015">We don't like </span><span class="cls_051">v</span><span class="cls_015">ing.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:86.23px;top:548.33px" class="cls_014"><span class="cls_014">Does she like you to complain?</span></div>
