<div style="position:absolute;left:324.73px;top:354.00px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">It was worth </span><span class="cls_053">v</span><span class="cls_011">ing.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:96.72px;top:367.80px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">- Wasn't it worth </span><span class="cls_053">v</span><span class="cls_011">ing?</span></div>
