<div style="position:absolute;left:172.38px;top:17.34px" class="cls_004"><span class="cls_004">LA BONTE’S TOP 100 ENGLISH CONVERSATION PATTERNS</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:557.58px;top:17.22px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">32</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:180.36px;top:67.14px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">I AM SUPPOSED TO </span><span class="cls_056">v</span><span class="cls_003">.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:138.66px;top:94.80px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">I AM SUPPOSED TO BE </span><span class="cls_056">v</span><span class="cls_003">ING.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:36.72px;top:153.78px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">1.  </span><span class="cls_011">I AM TO </span><span class="cls_053">v</span><span class="cls_011">.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:54.72px;top:167.58px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">In the past and present tense, there is short form to this pattern. It is not used in a negative sentence,</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:54.72px;top:181.38px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">positive question or negative question. I AM SUPPOSED TO is used much more.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:92.20px;top:208.98px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">(present)</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:158.19px;top:208.98px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">He is to go there today.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:324.71px;top:208.98px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">=</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:367.45px;top:208.98px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">He is supposed to go there today.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:158.22px;top:222.78px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">I am to talk to him later.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:324.72px;top:222.78px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">=</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:367.50px;top:222.78px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">I am supposed to talk to him later.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:92.22px;top:236.58px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">(past)</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:158.26px;top:236.58px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">They were to see him today.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:324.73px;top:236.58px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">=</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:367.50px;top:236.58px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">They were supposed to see him today.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:158.22px;top:250.38px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">She was to buy it there.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:324.79px;top:250.38px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">=</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:367.50px;top:250.38px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">She was supposed to be buy it there.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:36.72px;top:277.98px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">2.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:63.72px;top:277.98px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">I AM DUE TO </span><span class="cls_053">v</span><span class="cls_011">.</span><span class="cls_002">  This is another variation.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:86.22px;top:305.58px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">(past)</span></div>
