<div style="position:absolute;left:86.22px;top:643.62px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">Aren't you thinking about dating her?</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:324.72px;top:643.62px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">Yes, I'm thinking about dating her.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:86.22px;top:657.42px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">Where are you thinking about sleeping?</span></div>
