<div style="position:absolute;left:86.22px;top:671.22px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">What is she thinking about playing?</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:324.72px;top:671.22px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">She's thinking about playing cards.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:86.22px;top:685.02px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">When are they thinking about coming?</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:324.72px;top:685.02px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">They're thinking about coming tomorrow.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:86.22px;top:698.82px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">Who are you thinking about writing to?</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:324.75px;top:698.82px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">I'm thinking about writing to my dad.</span></div>
