<div style="position:absolute;left:324.74px;top:422.88px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">Yes, she felt like crying.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:86.22px;top:436.68px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">What did he feel like making?</span></div>
