<div style="position:absolute;left:63.72px;top:661.67px" class="cls_014"><span class="cls_014">She </span><span class="cls_015">nearly </span><span class="cls_014">got ready to drive him.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:288.65px;top:661.67px" class="cls_014"><span class="cls_014">I was </span><span class="cls_015">just about</span><span class="cls_014"> in the middle of going to sleep.</span></div>
