<div style="position:absolute;left:36.72px;top:427.08px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">1.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:75.73px;top:427.08px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">All the patterns within each category of "a", "b" and "c" are the same.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.72px;top:440.88px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">It's alright to take it.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:212.23px;top:440.88px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">It's ok not to go.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:365.26px;top:440.88px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">It isn't alright to buy.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.72px;top:454.68px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">It's ok to take it.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:212.27px;top:454.68px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">It's alright not to go.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:365.28px;top:454.68px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">It isn't ok to buy.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.72px;top:468.48px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">It's alright if you take it.</span></div>
