<div style="position:absolute;left:36.72px;top:509.82px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">2.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:59.24px;top:509.82px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">All patterns can be used in the present, past and future tense.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.72px;top:523.62px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">(present)</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:144.68px;top:523.62px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">Is it ok to leave?</span></div>
