<div style="position:absolute;left:72.72px;top:551.22px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">(future)</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:144.74px;top:551.22px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">Will it be ok to eat that?</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:311.27px;top:551.22px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">Yes, it'll be ok to eat that.</span></div>
