<div style="position:absolute;left:59.22px;top:578.82px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">If you want to insert a person's name, noun or object pronoun, this is how you insert it.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.72px;top:592.62px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">a.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:111.06px;top:592.62px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">It is ok </span><span class="cls_011">FOR</span><span class="cls_002"> </span><span class="cls_054">n/op</span><span class="cls_002"> to </span><span class="cls_054">v</span><span class="cls_002">.</span></div>
