<div style="position:absolute;left:47.77px;top:374.27px" class="cls_014"><span class="cls_014">2.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.53px;top:374.27px" class="cls_014"><span class="cls_014">NOT can be added before "</span><span class="cls_050">v</span><span class="cls_014">ing" to make a double negative.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:108.72px;top:386.94px" class="cls_014"><span class="cls_014">There is no sense in </span><span class="cls_015">not </span><span class="cls_014">giving it to him.</span></div>
