<div style="position:absolute;left:47.76px;top:412.26px" class="cls_014"><span class="cls_014">3.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.51px;top:412.26px" class="cls_014"><span class="cls_014">Here are some general questions related to this pattern:</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:108.73px;top:424.92px" class="cls_015"><span class="cls_015">WHAT SENSE DOES IT MAKE TO </span><span class="cls_051">v</span><span class="cls_015">?</span><span class="cls_014"> </span><span class="cls_015">  =  WHAT IS THE</span><span class="cls_051"> POINT</span><span class="cls_015"> IN/OF </span><span class="cls_051">v</span><span class="cls_015">ING?</span></div>
