<div style="position:absolute;left:47.76px;top:513.41px" class="cls_014"><span class="cls_014">4.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:67.00px;top:513.41px" class="cls_014"><span class="cls_014">Variations of </span><span class="cls_015">THERE IS NO SENSE IN </span><span class="cls_051">v</span><span class="cls_015">ING </span><span class="cls_014">are: </span><span class="cls_015">  IT DOESN'T MAKE ANY SENSE TO </span><span class="cls_051">v</span><span class="cls_015">.</span></div>
