<div style="position:absolute;left:210.84px;top:280.44px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">PATTERN + BE </span><span class="cls_056">a</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:36.72px;top:323.34px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">1.  Instead of adding a verb to a pattern, you can add "</span><span class="cls_011">BE </span><span class="cls_053">a</span><span class="cls_002">".</span></div>
