<div style="position:absolute;left:360.74px;top:378.54px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">She's going to </span><span class="cls_011">be </span><span class="cls_002">really</span><span class="cls_011"> angr</span><span class="cls_002">y.</span></div>
