<div style="position:absolute;left:36.72px;top:628.62px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">A verb becomes a noun by adding "</span><span class="cls_011">ING</span><span class="cls_002">”.  Drop "</span><span class="cls_011">E</span><span class="cls_002">" at the end of a verb when you add "</span><span class="cls_011">ING</span><span class="cls_002">."</span></div>
