<div style="position:absolute;left:288.75px;top:202.08px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">Yes, he became mad.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:109.62px;top:215.88px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">When did it get cold?</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:288.72px;top:215.88px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">It got cold last night.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:36.72px;top:243.60px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">PRESENT</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:109.70px;top:243.60px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">+  Does she get </span><span class="cls_053">a</span><span class="cls_011">?</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:288.72px;top:243.60px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">He becomes </span><span class="cls_053">a</span><span class="cls_011">.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:109.62px;top:257.40px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">-  Don't you become </span><span class="cls_053">a</span><span class="cls_011">?</span></div>
