<div style="position:absolute;left:109.62px;top:284.88px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">Does she get nervous?</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:288.70px;top:284.88px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">Yes, she gets nervous.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:109.62px;top:298.68px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">Don't you become tired?</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:288.73px;top:298.68px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">No, I don't become tired.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:36.72px;top:326.40px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">FUTURE</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:109.68px;top:326.40px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">+  Will she get </span><span class="cls_053">a</span><span class="cls_011">?</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:288.72px;top:326.40px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">He won't become </span><span class="cls_053">a</span><span class="cls_011">.</span></div>
