<div style="position:absolute;left:42.72px;top:330.18px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">DEPENDING ON/UPON </span><span class="cls_053">WHAT</span><span class="cls_011">  s</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:108.72px;top:349.86px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">DEPENDING ON  is the same as  DEPENDING UPON.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:108.72px;top:363.66px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">Instead of WHAT, you can use WHO, WHEN, WHERE and HOW.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:144.72px;top:377.58px" class="cls_014"><span class="cls_014">Depending on what she says, I'll be able to go.</span></div>
