<div style="position:absolute;left:108.72px;top:454.50px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">This pattern can be made into a sentence using IT DEPENDS ON. It is usually</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:108.72px;top:468.30px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">used as a short answer to a question.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:144.72px;top:482.10px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">Do you want to go?</span></div>
