<div style="position:absolute;left:264.72px;top:215.88px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">She was there </span><span class="cls_011">the week </span><span class="cls_002">I was on vacation.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:114.72px;top:229.68px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">THE MONTH s</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:264.72px;top:229.68px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">The month</span><span class="cls_002"> I started to work there, they fired John.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:114.72px;top:243.48px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">THE YEAR s</span></div>
