<div style="position:absolute;left:114.72px;top:257.28px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">THE TIME s</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:264.72px;top:257.28px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">She really didn't look good </span><span class="cls_011">the time</span><span class="cls_002"> I saw her last.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:114.72px;top:271.08px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">THE NIGHT s</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:265.62px;top:271.08px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">The night</span><span class="cls_002"> he was here, he made dinner for everyone.</span></div>
