<div style="position:absolute;left:270.72px;top:284.88px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">I saw her </span><span class="cls_011">the morning</span><span class="cls_002"> I went to church.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:114.72px;top:298.68px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">THE AFTERNOON s</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:269.40px;top:298.68px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">She met him </span><span class="cls_011">the afternoon</span><span class="cls_002"> she first moved here.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:36.72px;top:326.34px" class="cls_009"><span class="cls_009">PAST</span></div>
