<div style="position:absolute;left:36.72px;top:76.20px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">1.  a & d & j   EVER is sometimes dropped. The beginning student should use EVER.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:162.72px;top:90.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">Is she </span><span class="cls_011">ever</span><span class="cls_002"> popular!</span></div>
