<div style="position:absolute;left:324.76px;top:311.34px" class="cls_005"><span class="cls_005">They don't know that he's rich.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:36.72px;top:335.28px" class="cls_005"><span class="cls_005">c.</span></div>
