<div style="position:absolute;left:180.68px;top:346.80px" class="cls_005"><span class="cls_005">Do you know if he came?</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:324.70px;top:346.80px" class="cls_005"><span class="cls_005">I can't tell if he's sad or not.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:36.72px;top:370.74px" class="cls_005"><span class="cls_005">d.</span></div>
