<div style="position:absolute;left:172.38px;top:17.34px" class="cls_004"><span class="cls_004">LA BONTE’S TOP 100 ENGLISH CONVERSATION PATTERNS</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:551.58px;top:17.22px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">130</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:141.36px;top:34.98px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">HOW MUCH DOES IT COST?</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:36.72px;top:87.24px" class="cls_015"><span class="cls_015">a.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:59.24px;top:87.24px" class="cls_015"><span class="cls_015">How much is it?</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:243.74px;top:87.24px" class="cls_015"><span class="cls_015">It is </span><span class="cls_051">$$</span><span class="cls_015">.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:59.22px;top:99.90px" class="cls_015"><span class="cls_015">How much is it to </span><span class="cls_051">v</span><span class="cls_015">?</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:243.74px;top:99.90px" class="cls_015"><span class="cls_015">It is </span><span class="cls_051">$$</span><span class="cls_015"> to </span><span class="cls_051">v</span><span class="cls_015">.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:59.22px;top:112.56px" class="cls_015"><span class="cls_015">Is it </span><span class="cls_051">$$</span><span class="cls_015"> to </span><span class="cls_051">v</span><span class="cls_015">?</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:243.75px;top:112.56px" class="cls_015"><span class="cls_015">Yes, it is </span><span class="cls_051">$$</span><span class="cls_015"> to </span><span class="cls_051">v</span><span class="cls_015">.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:378.77px;top:112.56px" class="cls_015"><span class="cls_015">No, it isn't </span><span class="cls_051">$$</span><span class="cls_015"> to </span><span class="cls_051">v</span><span class="cls_015">.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:59.22px;top:125.22px" class="cls_015"><span class="cls_015">How much is it for </span><span class="cls_051">n</span><span class="cls_015">?</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:243.72px;top:125.22px" class="cls_015"><span class="cls_015">It is </span><span class="cls_051">$$ </span><span class="cls_015"> for </span><span class="cls_051">n</span><span class="cls_015">.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:378.72px;top:125.22px" class="cls_015"><span class="cls_015">=</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:412.56px;top:125.22px" class="cls_051"><span class="cls_051">n</span><span class="cls_015"> is</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:439.71px;top:125.22px" class="cls_051"><span class="cls_051">$$</span><span class="cls_015">.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:108.71px;top:137.81px" class="cls_014"><span class="cls_014">How much is that radio?</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:324.77px;top:137.81px" class="cls_014"><span class="cls_014">That radio is $15.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:108.71px;top:150.41px" class="cls_014"><span class="cls_014">Was it $7.50 to get into the movies?</span></div>
