<div style="position:absolute;left:36.71px;top:477.59px" class="cls_014"><span class="cls_014">2.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:59.20px;top:477.59px" class="cls_014"><span class="cls_014">Instead of cash, you can buy things with a check or a credit card.</span></div>
