<div style="position:absolute;left:290.45px;top:490.32px" class="cls_015"><span class="cls_015">=</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:324.26px;top:490.32px" class="cls_015"><span class="cls_015">Can I pay by check?</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:108.72px;top:502.98px" class="cls_015"><span class="cls_015">Do you take credit cards?</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:290.39px;top:502.98px" class="cls_015"><span class="cls_015">=</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:324.20px;top:502.98px" class="cls_015"><span class="cls_015">Can I charge it?</span></div>
