<div style="position:absolute;left:173.22px;top:408.60px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">ANYBODY TO </span><span class="cls_053">v</span><span class="cls_011">.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:324.72px;top:408.60px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">Don't you have anybody to take?</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:173.22px;top:436.20px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">ANYTIME TO </span><span class="cls_053">v</span><span class="cls_011">.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:324.73px;top:436.20px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">Isn't there anytime to discuss this?</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:173.22px;top:450.00px" class="cls_053"><span class="cls_053">THE</span><span class="cls_011"> TIME TO </span><span class="cls_053">v</span><span class="cls_011">.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:324.73px;top:450.00px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">I don't have time to clean the room.</span></div>
