<div style="position:absolute;left:173.22px;top:532.80px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">ANY </span><span class="cls_053">n</span><span class="cls_011"> TO </span><span class="cls_053">v</span><span class="cls_011">.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:324.72px;top:532.80px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">I don't have any money to give her.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.72px;top:544.62px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">**Do not use in a positive sentence. Use only in -S, +Q or -Q.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:36.72px;top:558.12px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">c.***</span></div>
