<div style="position:absolute;left:36.72px;top:253.38px" class="cls_014"><span class="cls_014">1.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:56.01px;top:253.38px" class="cls_014"><span class="cls_014">This pattern can be used in a -Q, +Q, -S or +S.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:167.22px;top:266.04px" class="cls_015"><span class="cls_015">+Q</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:220.59px;top:266.04px" class="cls_014"><span class="cls_014">Do you have a lot to complain about?</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:167.22px;top:278.70px" class="cls_015"><span class="cls_015">-Q</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:220.59px;top:278.70px" class="cls_014"><span class="cls_014">Doesn't she have a lot of things to send?</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:167.22px;top:291.36px" class="cls_015"><span class="cls_015">-S</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:221.00px;top:291.36px" class="cls_014"><span class="cls_014">I haven't got a lot of time to talk.</span></div>
