<div style="position:absolute;left:220.88px;top:303.95px" class="cls_014"><span class="cls_014">She had a lot of people to get a hold of.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:36.72px;top:316.61px" class="cls_014"><span class="cls_014">2.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:56.00px;top:316.61px" class="cls_014"><span class="cls_014">You can substitute other nouns for </span><span class="cls_015">THINGS</span><span class="cls_014">, </span><span class="cls_015">PEOPLE</span><span class="cls_014">, or</span><span class="cls_015"> PLACES</span><span class="cls_014">.</span></div>
