<div style="position:absolute;left:321.96px;top:582.23px" class="cls_014"><span class="cls_014">He had</span><span class="cls_015"> a few</span><span class="cls_014"> places to show her.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:72.73px;top:594.89px" class="cls_014"><span class="cls_014">I didn't have anything </span><span class="cls_015">for her </span><span class="cls_014">to take.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:322.01px;top:594.89px" class="cls_014"><span class="cls_014">They had a lot of places</span><span class="cls_015"> for us </span><span class="cls_014">to work.</span></div>
