<div style="position:absolute;left:36.72px;top:700.32px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">I didn't go anyplace he said was dangerous.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:262.88px;top:700.32px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">=    I didn't go anyplace </span><span class="cls_011">which</span><span class="cls_002"> he said was dangerous.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:36.72px;top:714.12px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">I forgot something he told me.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:264.74px;top:714.12px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">=    I forgot something </span><span class="cls_011">that</span><span class="cls_002"> he told me.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:36.72px;top:727.92px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">I met somebody</span><span class="cls_011"> who</span><span class="cls_002"> stayed here yesterday.</span></div>
