<div style="position:absolute;left:36.72px;top:567.66px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">1. With "a.", THAT, WHICH and WHO are optional.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:144.72px;top:581.46px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">I called anytime </span><span class="cls_011">that</span><span class="cls_002"> I had time.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:330.30px;top:581.46px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">=</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:361.08px;top:581.46px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">I called anytime I had time.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:36.72px;top:595.26px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">2. With "b.", THAT, WHICH and WHO are necessary when used as the subject of the sentence or</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:36.72px;top:609.06px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">question.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:144.72px;top:622.86px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">I ate anything </span><span class="cls_011">that</span><span class="cls_002"> was sweet.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:144.72px;top:636.66px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">I ate anything was sweet.</span><span class="cls_011"> (wrong)</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:144.72px;top:650.46px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">She called anyone </span><span class="cls_011">who</span><span class="cls_002"> was disappointed.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:144.72px;top:664.26px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">She called anyone was disappointed. </span><span class="cls_011">(wrong)</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:144.72px;top:678.06px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">Did she read anything</span><span class="cls_011"> that</span><span class="cls_002"> was in English?</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:144.72px;top:691.86px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">Didn't you meet anyone </span><span class="cls_011">that </span><span class="cls_002">was friendly?</span></div>
