<div style="position:absolute;left:36.72px;top:146.70px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">1.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:59.20px;top:146.70px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">WHO and THAT are interchangeable:</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:252.79px;top:146.70px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">I like the girl </span><span class="cls_005">who </span><span class="cls_012">studies there.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:255.72px;top:158.22px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">I like the girl </span><span class="cls_005">that</span><span class="cls_012"> studies there.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:36.72px;top:169.69px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">2.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:59.22px;top:169.69px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">Note the change in tense:</span></div>
