<div style="position:absolute;left:252.72px;top:169.69px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">He took the boy who </span><span class="cls_005">comes </span><span class="cls_012">here.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:180.72px;top:181.21px" class="cls_005"><span class="cls_005">past</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:252.72px;top:181.21px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">She wrote to her brother who </span><span class="cls_005">lived</span><span class="cls_012"> in Chicago.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:180.72px;top:192.73px" class="cls_005"><span class="cls_005">v PP</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:252.72px;top:192.73px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">The guy that </span><span class="cls_005">has lived </span><span class="cls_012">there went on vacation.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:180.72px;top:204.19px" class="cls_005"><span class="cls_005">future</span></div>
