<div style="position:absolute;left:36.72px;top:215.72px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">3.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:59.22px;top:215.72px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">Add "</span><span class="cls_005">s</span><span class="cls_012">" to the verb with 3rd person singular, present tense:</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:321.01px;top:215.72px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">The girl who</span><span class="cls_005"> comes</span><span class="cls_012"> here likes you.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:318.78px;top:227.24px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">She contacted the mechanic who</span><span class="cls_005"> fixes </span><span class="cls_012">the cars.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:36.72px;top:238.70px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">4.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:64.25px;top:238.68px" class="cls_005"><span class="cls_005">THE PERSON v</span><span class="cls_048">ING</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:164.88px;top:238.68px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">=   </span><span class="cls_005">THE PERSON WHO IS </span><span class="cls_048">v</span><span class="cls_005">ING</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:181.80px;top:250.32px" class="cls_005"><span class="cls_005">THE PERSON THAT IS  vING</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:59.22px;top:261.72px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">a.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:81.19px;top:261.72px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">When you imply continuous action (I AM vING), this short form is used a lot.  </span><span class="cls_005">THE PERSON </span><span class="cls_048">v</span><span class="cls_005">ING</span><span class="cls_012"> can be</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:161.76px;top:273.18px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">used in the present, past and future tenses.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:95.22px;top:284.71px" class="cls_005"><span class="cls_005">present</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:154.73px;top:284.71px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">The guy com</span><span class="cls_005">ing</span><span class="cls_012"> tonight is funny.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:309.13px;top:284.71px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">=</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:339.80px;top:284.71px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">The guy who is funny is coming tonight.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:95.22px;top:296.17px" class="cls_005"><span class="cls_005">past</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:154.72px;top:296.17px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">The driver tak</span><span class="cls_005">ing</span><span class="cls_012"> the test failed.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:308.73px;top:296.17px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">=</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:339.39px;top:296.17px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">The driver who was taking the test failed.</span></div>
