<div style="position:absolute;left:144.71px;top:672.49px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">He played cards with </span><span class="cls_005">those who</span><span class="cls_012"> he knew.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:324.66px;top:672.49px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">=</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:360.66px;top:672.49px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">He played cards with </span><span class="cls_005">the men</span><span class="cls_012"> he knew.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:94.24px;top:683.95px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">(singular)   Did you see </span><span class="cls_005">who </span><span class="cls_012">I was with?</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:324.67px;top:683.95px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">=</span></div>
