<div style="position:absolute;left:36.72px;top:332.10px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">1.</span><span class="cls_005">  </span><span class="cls_048">THAT</span><span class="cls_012"> and </span><span class="cls_048">WHICH</span><span class="cls_012"> are optional.  In most cases, they are dropped.</span></div>
