<div style="position:absolute;left:36.74px;top:378.06px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">2. </span><span class="cls_005"> WHAT s</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:112.30px;top:378.06px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">This is used instead of THE THING </span><span class="cls_049">THAT s</span><span class="cls_012"> and THE THING </span><span class="cls_049">WHICH s</span><span class="cls_012">.  It is generally used only</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:76.80px;top:389.58px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">as the object of the sentence/question.  It is not used as much as THE THING THAT s and THE THING WHICH s.</span></div>
